#. Tag: title
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kded6</command> consolidates several small services in one process. "
"These are mostly &DBus; services provided by KDED modules, but it also "
"manages sycoca (a binary cache of servicetypes, &MIME; types and services "
"used by KService) and KConfig update scripts as needed."
msgstr ""
"<command>kded6</command> združuje več majhnih storitev v enem procesu.To so "
"večinoma storitve &DBus;, ki jih zagotavljajo moduli KDED, ampak "
"tudiupravlja sycoca (binarni predpomnilnik vrst storitev, vrst &MIME; in "
"storitev, ki jih uporablja KService) in KConfig po potrebi posodobi skripte."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For sycoca, it monitors the directories containing .desktop files. When a "
"file is added/removed, it waits 5 seconds (in case of a series of updates), "
"and then launches <command>kbuildsycoca6</command> to update the sycoca."
msgstr ""
"Za sycoca nadzoruje imenike, ki vsebujejo datoteke .desktop. Ko je datoteka "
"dodana/odstranjena, počaka 5 sekund (v primeru niza posodobitev),in nato "
"zažene <command>kbuildsycoca6</command> za posodobitev sycoca."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For KConfig, it checks newly-installed update files, &ie; the *.upd files "
"used to update configuration files of users when the configuration file "
"formats changes, and runs the KConfig update utility to perform the updates."
msgstr ""
"Pri programu KConfig preveri novo nameščene datoteke posodobitev, &ie; "
"datoteke *.upd, ki se uporabljajo za posodabljanje konfiguracijskih datotek "
"uporabnikov, ko se spremenijo formati konfiguracijskih datotek, in za "
"izvajanje posodobitev zažene pripomoček za posodabljanje programa KConfig."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Those tasks are also run when <command>kded6</command> is started to ensure "
"that the user configuration is up to date."
msgstr ""
"Ta opravila se izvajajo tudi, ko se zažene <command>kded6</command>, da se "
"zagotovida je uporabniška konfiguracija posodobljena."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You do not normally need to run <command>kded6</command> directly; &plasma; "
"desktop sessions run it automatically, and it is started on demand when an "
"application attempts to use a &DBus; interface provided by it or one of its "
"modules."
msgstr ""
"Običajno vam <command>kded6</command> ni treba zaganjati neposredno; &plasma;"
"namizne seje ga zaženejo samodejno in se zažene na zahtevo, ko aplikacija "
"poskuša uporabiti &DBus; vmesnik, ki ga ponuja sam ali eden od njegovih "
"modulov."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "--check"
msgstr "--check"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the sycoca database, updating it if necessary, and exit."
msgstr ""
"Preverite zbirko podatkov sycoca, jo po potrebi posodobite in zaključite."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kded6</command> can be configured with the <filename>kded5rc</"
"filename> ini-style configuration file. On &UNIX; systems, this can be found "
"at <filename><varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname>/kded5rc</filename>; if "
"<varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname> is not set, this defaults to "
"<filename>~/.config/kded5rc</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<command>kded6</command> je mogoče konfigurirati z <filename>kded5rc</"
"filename> konfiguracijska datoteka v slogu ini. Na sistemih &UNIX; je to "
"mogoče najtina <filename><varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname>/kded5rc</"
"filename>; če<varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname> ni nastavljeno, to je "
"privzeto<filename>~/.config/kded5rc</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configuration file entries are read on-demand, so changes can be made while "
"<command>kded6</command> is running. However, all the current configuration "
"options only really affect the startup behaviour of <command>kded6</command>."
msgstr ""
"Vnosi v konfiguracijski datoteki se berejo na zahtevo, tako da je mogoče "
"spreminjati med tem ko se <command>kded6</command> izvaja. Vendar pa vse "
"trenutne možnosti konfiguracije resnično vplivajo le na obnašanje "
"<command>kded6</command> ob zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <option>[General]</option> section has the following options:"
msgstr "V razdelku <option>[Glavno]</option> so naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckSycoca"
msgstr "PreveriSycoca"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to update sycoca at startup (default: <constant>true</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se ob zagonu posodobi sycoca (privzeto: <constant>resnično</"
"constant>)."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckUpdates"
msgstr "PreveriPosodobitve"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to perform outstanding KConfig updates at startup (default: "
"<constant>true</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se ob zagonu izvedejo neplačane posodobitve KConfig (privzeto: "
"<constant>resnično</constant>)."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckFileStamps"
msgstr "PreveriŽigeDatoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to check file timestamps when performing the initial sycoca update "
"(default: <constant>true</constant>). See the documentation for "
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Ali se pri izvajanju začetne posodobitve sycoca preverijo časovni žigi "
"datotek(privzeto: <constant>true</constant>). Oglejte si dokumentacijo "
"za<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> za več podrobnosti."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "DelayedCheck"
msgstr "ZamaknjenoPreverjanje"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to delay the initial sycoca update until about a minute after "
"starting (default: <constant>false</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se začetna posodobitev programa sycoca odloži na približno minuto po "
"začetku (privzeto: <constant>false</constant>)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each module also has a <option>[Module-<replaceable>name</replaceable>]</"
"option> section in <filename>kded5rc</filename>, where <replaceable>name</"
"replaceable> is the name of the module's desktop file without the <filename>."
"desktop</filename> extension. This contains an <option>autoload</option> "
"option that specifies whether the module should be automatically loaded when "
"<command>kded6</command> is started (default: <constant>false</constant>). "
"Note that this setting can also be changed via <command>kded6</command>'s "
"&DBus; interface."
msgstr ""
"Vsak modul ima tudi <option>[Module-<replaceable>name</replaceable>]</"
"option> v <filename>kded5rc</filename>, kjer je <replaceable>name</"
"replaceable> ime datoteke namizja modula brez podaljška <filename>.desktop</"
"filename>. To vsebuje <option>autoload</option> možnost, ki določa, ali naj "
"se modul samodejno naloži, ko je <command>kded6</command> zagnan (privzeto: "
"<constant>false</constant>). Upoštevajte, da lahko to nastavitev spremenite "
"tudi prek <command>kded6</command> vmesnika &DBus;."

